                     <interp inst="t18281023-160-person877" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the officer. When I came up the prosecutor had the prisoner by the collar, and the mutton was on the board; I asked him how he came to do it - he said he found it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was not in front of the shop at all till he brought me there.</p>
